    // MODERN VARIATION - 41%
    2... Nf3 3. Bb5+                    // +0.24 - Bb5+ is less common but has a higher winrate and is more forcing. 
                                        // the main move, d4, scores +0.32, but Bg5+ avoids the Bg5 response to d4, which has a low winrate 
                                        // all 3 of these lines winrates are 16-23% higher than the opponents 

